I would like you to be clear that

00:01:13.340 --> 00:01:14.800
if we had to choose one method

00:01:14.800 --> 00:01:16.560
we would actually have to choose

00:01:16.560 --> 00:01:17.980
cash flow discount and for

00:01:17.980 --> 00:01:19.620
a number of reasons.

00:01:20.080 --> 00:01:22.300
One of them is because it is probably

00:01:22.300 --> 00:01:23.080
the most real.

00:01:24.360 --> 00:01:26.940
Real is a very broad word,

00:01:27.020 --> 00:01:28.080
but what do I mean by this?

00:01:29.320 --> 00:01:30.780
You think one thing, when you

00:01:30.780 --> 00:01:32.960
buy a business or when you invest

00:01:32.960 --> 00:01:34.840
in a business or an asset, it

