doesn't matter in any investment,

00:01:36.020 --> 00:01:38.580
in the bottom, what you

00:01:38.580 --> 00:01:41.420
are buying is the hope of getting

00:01:41.420 --> 00:01:43.820
some future cash flows.

00:01:45.180 --> 00:01:46.660
You do is commit some current

00:01:46.660 --> 00:01:48.280
cash flows, which is your investment,

00:01:48.280 --> 00:01:50.340
with the hope of receiving in

00:01:50.340 --> 00:01:53.340
the future some cash flows

00:01:53.340 --> 00:01:54.300
that can be via dividends,

00:01:54.300 --> 00:01:56.680
give me equal or via sale

