00:01:58.780 --> 00:01:59.600
value, etc.

00:02:01.120 --> 00:02:02.820
And it is that this is exactly

00:02:02.820 --> 00:02:04.300
what we will value, what we will

00:02:04.300 --> 00:02:06.220
value is that, is that you

00:02:06.220 --> 00:02:08.220
will actually get or not get those

00:02:08.220 --> 00:02:10.320
