00:02:10.800 --> 00:02:13.680
It is therefore more oriented

00:02:13.680 --> 00:02:15.080
to the real interests or the

00:02:15.080 --> 00:02:17.860
real goals of the buyer.

00:02:18.100 --> 00:02:19.360
Benefit number two.

00:02:19.940 --> 00:02:21.780
With the cash flow discount, we

00:02:21.780 --> 00:02:22.860
will calculate the intrinsic

00:02:22.860 --> 00:02:24.420
value of our company.

