We will only measure ourselves

00:02:51.360 --> 00:02:53.880
and we will project, estimate

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:55.180
what cash flows we will

00:02:55.180 --> 00:02:56.300
generate.

00:02:56.300 --> 00:02:57.760
So we will calculate the intrinsic

00:02:57.760 --> 00:02:58.800
value of our company and

00:02:58.800 --> 00:03:01.720
another benefit is that it

00:03:01.720 --> 00:03:03.600
